OL,6,FRyan Lowry, a tree surgeon and foster
OL,7,Fparent from Partington in , was struck
OL,8,F13 times with an axe by his cousin
OL,9,FAshley Glennon, a paranoid
OL,10,Fschizophrenic with a history of
OL,11,Fviolence on 27 February 2020.
OL,13,FRyan's wife, Michelle, said:
OL,14,F"Everything is different now, the
OL,15,Fwhole world has changed. You lead
OL,16,Fcompletely different lives."
