OL,6,FAn inquest at Stockport Coroners Court
OL,7,Fheard how he was under the care of the
OL,8,FGreater Manchester Health Trust while
OL,9,Falso being supervised by 's (GMP)
OL,10,FSexual Offender Management team.
OL,12,FDespite this, both organisations
OL,13,Ffailed to share information on Glennon
OL,14,Fand missed several opportunities to
OL,15,Fprevent Ryan Lowry's death.
OL,17,FMichelle said: "(Ashley) had several
OL,18,Fserious relapses of increasing levels
OL,19,Fof violence in the time coming up to
OL,20,Fit. The information was there, it just
OL,21,Fwasn't acted on."
