OL,6,FThe day before Ryan was killed,
OL,7,FGlennon had smashed a window and
OL,8,Fkicked in a door at his ex-partners
OL,9,Fhouse.JWhen Glennon's ex-partner rang
OL,10,Fthe police to tell them what happened,
OL,11,Fshe was put on hold for 40 minutes
OL,12,Fbefore being disconnected.
OL,14,FMeanwhile Ryan, worried about his
OL,15,Fcousin's mental state, had contacted
OL,16,Fhis mental health team.JThey spoke to
OL,17,FGlennon by phone, but failed to pass
OL,18,Fon any information to GMP.
