OL,6,FMichelle said: "They didn't ask him
OL,7,Fabout the incident earlier in the day.
OL,8,FHe portrayed himself as being in a
OL,9,Fmuch better position than he was in."
OL,11,FRyan's brother, Daniel, added: "There
OL,12,Fwas just missed opportunities on all
OL,13,Flevels"
