OL,6,FThat evening, Ryan went to check on
OL,7,Fhis cousin, who chased him out onto a
OL,8,Fstreet and killed him with an axe.
OL,9,FGlennon, then aged 32, pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto manslaughter by reason of
OL,11,Fdiminished responsibility and was
OL,12,Fsentenced to an indefinite hospital
OL,13,Forder in January 2021.
OL,15,FRyan's family are being supported by
OL,16,FJulian Hendy from the Hundred
OL,17,FFamilies, a charity which provides
OL,18,Finformation and practical advice for
OL,19,Ffamilies bereaved by people with
OL,20,Fmental health problemsJHe says this
OL,21,Fcase is just the tip of the iceberg.
