OL,6,FHe said: "I've documented over 250
OL,7,Fhomicides by people with serious
OL,8,Fillnesses in the north west since 1993.
OL,10,F"Often it's a failure to assess risk
OL,11,Fproperly... These are people that can
OL,12,Fbe dangerous when unwell or
OL,13,Funmedicated and people often don't
OL,14,Fappreciate that or act on what they
OL,15,Fknow."
