OL,6,FDr Arasu Kuppuswamy, Chief Medical
OL,7,FOfficer at Greater Manchester Mental
OL,8,FHealth NHS Foundation Trust said: "We
OL,9,Fexpress our deepest sympathies to Ryan
OL,10,FLowry's family and friends following
OL,11,Fhis tragic and untimely death.
OL,13,F"We are very sorry for the
OL,14,Fshortcomings in the standard of care
OL,15,Fand treatment we provided to Mr
OL,16,FGlennon.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/13
