OL,6,F"This includes implementing a new
OL,7,FClinical Risk Assessment and Safety
OL,8,FPlan Tool, which is being rolled out
OL,9,Facross the Trust following a
OL,10,Fsuccessful pilot, supported by a
OL,11,Fcomprehensive training package for
OL,12,Fstaff.
OL,14,F"Every local Division at GMMH now also
OL,15,Fhas its own dedicated Safeguarding
OL,16,FLead, to support and strengthen
OL,17,Fsafeguarding.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/13
