OL,6,F"And we have reviewed and improved our
OL,7,FTogether Strategy, to make sure that
OL,8,Fservice user and carer collaboration
OL,9,Fis at the heart of everything we do.
OL,11,F"We will continue to review this
OL,12,Fimportant work to ensure it is
OL,13,Fproperly embedded and built upon where
OL,14,Fnecessary."
OL,16,FIn a statement, Greater Manchester
OL,17,FPolice said: "Our thoughts and
OL,18,Fcondolences are with Mr Lowry's family
OL,19,Fat this difficult time.
