OL,6,F"We respect the findings of the Jury
OL,7,Fand acknowledge the comments made
OL,8,Fconcerning the handling of the 101
OL,9,Fcall made in this case, and Greater
OL,10,FManchester Police's Sex Offender
OL,11,FManagement Unit (SOMU).
OL,13,F"We recognise the importance of
OL,14,Feffective call handling and multi-
OL,15,Fagency information sharing and are
OL,16,Fcommitted to making further
OL,17,Fimprovements in these areas to better
OL,18,Fserve and protect the public.
