OL,6,F"Whilst of little consolation to Mr
OL,7,FLowry's family, technical issues
OL,8,Fwithin GMP's 101 system back in 2020
OL,9,Fhave been fixed, and calls to 101 now
OL,10,Ftake on average 54 seconds to be
OL,11,Fanswered.
OL,13,F"GMP's SOMU has also made significant
OL,14,Fprogress in reducing backlogs and
OL,15,Fimproving the timeliness of offender
OL,16,Fvisits."
